I know it's not enough to convict.
but it is enough to open an investigation.

264
00:20:41.074 --> 00:20:43.535
You got pictures of Max.
uh. talking to the girl.

265
00:20:43.619 --> 00:20:45.579
- the girl who he said he never met.
- Yeah.

266
00:20:45.662 --> 00:20:47.039
