298
00:22:08.745 --> 00:22:09.746
No. no…

299
00:22:09.830 --> 00:22:11.874
- I wanna rule some things out.
- No. Gray...

300
00:22:11.957 --> 00:22:14.209
Tom. we need to rule some things out.

301
00:22:14.293 --> 00:22:17.337
You know. I think you should probably
make an appointment with our attorney.

302
00:22:18.630 --> 00:22:19.965
- Come on.
- Yeah.

303
00:22:20.048 --> 00:22:22.259
Tom. were you involved in
Ray Rawlins's murder?

304
00:22:23.302 --> 00:22:24.428
Jesus. man.

305
00:22:24.511 --> 00:22:26.013
