- Tom.

306
00:22:26.096 --> 00:22:28.307
- You think that I killed a family friend?
- Tom.

307
00:22:28.390 --> 00:22:29.683
Hang on. no. no.

308
00:22:29.766 --> 00:22:31.768
You think that I would let
my 17-year-old daughter…

309
00:22:31.852 --> 00:22:32.853
