It's on the registry and all.
but he threw it away years ago.

327
00:23:20.692 --> 00:23:22.778
Uh. nothing else. Not that we know of.

328
00:23:22.861 --> 00:23:26.281
but after talking to Grayson
it's pretty clear they're looking at Tom.

329
