- And you had the gun?

368
00:25:20.771 --> 00:25:23.857
Okay. Did you ever lose sight of it?
Was it ever in Max's hands?

369
00:25:23.941 --> 00:25:26.068
- No. No. I don't know. Dad.
- Did Max ever have the gun in his hands?

370
00:25:26.151 --> 00:25:27.986
- Nat. you gotta…
- It was in my bag.

371
00:25:28.070 --> 00:25:30.155
and I…
…but at some point. I fell asleep.

372
00:25:30.239 --> 00:25:32.241
Don't you make us
do this the hard way. Tom.

373
00:25:32.324 --> 00:25:33.575
Wait. Dad. Please. I...

374
00:25:33.659 --> 00:25:35.244
Okay. Everything's gonna be okay.

375
00:25:36.370 --> 00:25:39.289
You don't say anything to nobody. okay?

376
