386
00:26:08.110 --> 00:26:11.697
Tom. Tom. I'm gonna call Jared. all right?
We're gonna meet you down there.

387
00:26:13.156 --> 00:26:15.075
This isn't gonna stick.
We're gonna get you out.

388
00:26:47.733 --> 00:26:49.067
Come on. let's go inside.

389
00:26:55.115 --> 00:26:58.118
Attorney Anna Bowden. bar number 54481.

390
00:26:58.202 --> 00:27:04.791
calling to confirm a visit with my client.
Thomas Bowden. booking number M67052.

391
00:27:10.547 --> 00:27:13.926
We can prove that Tom Bowden conspired
to frame our client for possession.

392
00:27:14.009 --> 00:27:16.929
Now. unfortunately.
Ray Rawlins found out about this plan.

393
00:27:17.012 --> 00:27:18.805
and Tom Bowden killed him in cold-blood.

394
00:27:18.889 --> 00:27:21.391
intending to accuse my client
of that crime too.

395
00:27:21.475 --> 00:27:22.768
And you can back up these claims?

396
00:27:22.851 --> 00:27:25.062
Yeah. yeah. right from
the horse's mouth right here.

397
00:27:26.980 --> 00:27:32.945
Um. my son-in-law set out to frame Max.
and I helped him.

398
00:27:33.028 --> 00:27:34.947
Why? Because I'm a stupid old man

399
00:27:35.030 --> 00:27:37.866
who just wanted to get up with
his grandkids again. which was the deal.

400
00:27:38.951 --> 00:27:41.828
Then this Ray Rawlins guy…

401
00:27:42.621 --> 00:27:44.248
It's okay. It's okay.

402
00:27:44.331 --> 00:27:45.791
I don't know why…

403
00:27:45.874 --> 00:27:51.839
Look. I love my daughter. Anna.
and I would do anything for her.

404
00:27:52.548 --> 00:27:57.928
Anyway. Tom and Anna Bowden have
built a life of privilege.

405
00:27:58.011 --> 00:28:01.181
Built on my misery.
you know. my suffering.

406
00:28:01.265 --> 00:28:07.354
But they're not and they've never been
the good people they say they are.

407
00:28:07.437 --> 00:28:10.649
Tom Bowden did this. Look at this.

408
00:28:10.732 --> 00:28:13.902
Get close. Bring me the camera.
Bring the camera here.

409
00:28:13.986 --> 00:28:15.445
Come here. Look at that. yeah?

410
00:28:16.029 --> 00:28:17.865
