431
00:29:27.768 --> 00:29:29.853
You manipulated me. You got me.

432
00:29:29.937 --> 00:29:33.774
We put Max in jail
so that you wouldn't have to face him.

433
00:29:33.857 --> 00:29:37.152
I didn't force you to do anything.
You wanted him there as much as I did.

434
00:29:37.236 --> 00:29:40.155
How long were you gonna
hide this from me?

435
00:29:40.239 --> 00:29:41.406
What was the endgame?

436
00:29:41.490 --> 00:29:43.075
- Were you just gonna let it play out?
- No. I swear.

437
00:29:43.158 --> 00:29:45.327
- it's more complicated than that.
