457
00:31:43.195 --> 00:31:44.530
You need coffee.

458
00:31:58.710 --> 00:32:00.379
What did Max Cady do to you?

459
00:32:07.261 --> 00:32:09.388
This was me for the longest time.

460
00:32:11.431 --> 00:32:14.184
I started to have these blackouts. um…

461
00:32:16.979 --> 00:32:20.774
First it was just a. uh.
couple of hours. then…

462
