491
00:34:32.697 --> 00:34:33.907
But not deep enough.

492
00:34:38.536 --> 00:34:40.080
What do you mean. "buried"?

493
00:34:47.754 --> 00:34:48.880
It's okay.

494
00:34:49.922 --> 00:34:52.634
We'll find a way. I'll help you.

495
00:34:52.717 --> 00:34:56.929
No. What he's doing to us
is giving his life meaning.

496
00:35:00.392 --> 00:35:02.936
He's not gonna stop until we're dead.

497
00:35:06.523 --> 00:35:07.900
Or he is.

498
00:35:20.412 --> 00:35:22.289
I think you just need sleep.

499
00:35:24.124 --> 00:35:26.710
I'm so sorry.

500
00:35:26.793 --> 00:35:27.920
It's okay.

501
00:35:31.673 --> 00:35:32.966
Just lay down. Mom.

502
00:35:34.593 --> 00:35:35.594
It's okay.

503
00:36:11.046 --> 00:36:13.757
Oh.

504
00:36:23.976 --> 00:36:28.897
I miss you so much.
I miss you so much.

505
00:36:41.577 --> 00:36:43.245
Natalie. what are you doing here?

506
00:36:45.664 --> 00:36:47.291
You fucking used me.

507
00:36:47.875 --> 00:36:48.876
No.

508
00:36:50.169 --> 00:36:51.837
I-I didn't use you.

509
00:36:53.046 --> 00:36:55.841
I like you very much. Very much.

510
00:36:56.383 --> 00:36:58.385
I just want to help you be
who you really are.

511
00:36:58.969 --> 00:37:00.470
You care about me?

512
00:37:00.554 --> 00:37:02.890
Oh. yeah. yeah. A lot.

513
00:37:02.973 --> 00:37:04.391
Then go tell the truth.

514
00:37:05.559 --> 00:37:07.519
Tell the cops that my dad didn't kill Ray.

515
00:37:07.603 --> 00:37:09.730
What truth?

516
00:37:11.190 --> 00:37:12.316
Oh. the truth.

517
00:37:13.150 --> 00:37:16.737
Yeah. listen. you're about to learn things
about the people you love.

518
00:37:17.821 --> 00:37:19.198
Hard things. Natalie.

519
00:37:19.281 --> 00:37:22.743
Things that you are going to
wish you never knew.

520
00:37:23.452 --> 00:37:25.245
And it's gonna take time.

521
00:37:26.455 --> 00:37:29.958
Time…
…to really understand

522
00:37:31.668 --> 00:37:34.463
what is going on with you and them…

523
00:37:35.297 --> 00:37:36.798
But you will always have me.

524
00:37:37.883 --> 00:37:40.385
Always on your side.

525
00:37:40.469 --> 00:37:42.554
- Fuck you. I don't believe any of that.
- Hey!

526
00:37:42.638 --> 00:37:45.766
And I think you deserve everything
that happened to you.

527
00:37:45.849 --> 00:37:48.435
- All right.
- Everything!

528
00:37:49.061 --> 00:37:50.270
- Easy.
- Fuck you.

529
00:37:50.354 --> 00:37:52.105
Tell the truth.

530
00:37:52.981 --> 00:37:54.149
Give me that thing.

531
00:37:55.400 --> 00:37:56.777
Don't be a child.

532
00:37:56.860 --> 00:37:58.195
- Put that thing down.
- Stop.

533
00:37:58.904 --> 00:38:01.365
Move… I will fucking shoot you. Stop!

534
00:38:01.448 --> 00:38:02.741
You don't know how to use this thing.

535
00:38:02.824 --> 00:38:04.201
Fuck you.

536
00:38:04.284 --> 00:38:06.870
This thing can harm you. okay?

537
00:38:06.954 --> 00:38:08.205
Tell the truth.

538
00:38:08.288 --> 00:38:11.041
Look at your hands. They're shaking.

539
00:38:11.124 --> 00:38:14.711
My love. you can't do this.

540
00:38:22.553 --> 00:38:24.388
Or maybe you can shoot me.

541
00:38:25.764 --> 00:38:27.850
Maybe you can. It'll fix everything.

542
00:38:27.933 --> 00:38:29.059
Self-defense.

543
00:38:29.142 --> 00:38:31.103
- I'm a grown man. You're a child.
- Shut up.

544
00:38:31.186 --> 00:38:32.521
- You'll get away with that.
- Shut up.

545
00:38:32.604 --> 00:38:34.273
Yeah. and I'll be gone.
I'll be gone. I'll be gone.

546
00:38:34.356 --> 00:38:37.109
And you'll be back to your life
with your fucking weak father

547
00:38:37.192 --> 00:38:38.652
- and your horrible mother.
- I hate you.

548
00:38:38.735 --> 00:38:40.863
Hold on here. Yes. right here.

549
00:38:40.946 --> 00:38:42.990
- Fucking do it. Do it. Do it.
- Shut up.

550
00:38:43.699 --> 00:38:45.909
- Shut up. Shut up.
- Do it. Fucking do it. Pull the trigger.

551
00:38:45.993 --> 00:38:47.286
- Shut up! Shut up.
- Pull the trigger.

552
00:38:47.369 --> 00:38:48.787
- Do I need to beg? Do it!
- Stop!

553
00:38:56.712 --> 00:38:58.797
Fuck.

554
00:39:09.016 --> 00:39:12.352
- No. No. no. no. no. no. No. Natalie...
- Ma'am.

555
00:39:13.562 --> 00:39:14.813
No. no. no. no.

556
00:39:14.897 --> 00:39:17.608
- Mom? Mom!
- No. no. no. no. Natalie! Natalie!

557
00:39:17.691 --> 00:39:18.692
Ma'am. I will arrest you.

558
00:39:18.775 --> 00:39:20.027
Please let me go through.

559
00:39:20.110 --> 00:39:21.862
What happened. baby? What happened?

560
00:39:21.945 --> 00:39:23.113
I missed.

561
00:39:24.072 --> 00:39:25.782
No. No.

562
00:39:26.533 --> 00:39:27.534
I'm sorry.

563
00:39:28.994 --> 00:39:31.663
No. No. No. no. no. no. no.

564
00:39:31.747 --> 00:39:33.498
Don't take her! Please. Please. no.

565
00:39:33.582 --> 00:39:36.460
I did it. I did it. Look at me. I did it.

566
00:39:36.543 --> 00:39:37.669
Natalie.

567
00:39:38.170 --> 00:39:40.464
I love you. baby. okay?
You're fine.

568
00:39:41.465 --> 00:39:44.468
Natalie! Natalie!

569
00:40:03.654 --> 00:40:07.157
You're lucky to be alive.
Bullet missed all major organs.

570
00:40:10.536 --> 00:40:13.330
- You got a visitor.
- What?

571
00:40:13.413 --> 00:40:15.040
Your sister. Crystal.

572
00:40:15.666 --> 00:40:16.708
What?

573
00:40:23.006 --> 00:40:28.554
Oh. What are you doing here?

574
00:40:29.596 --> 00:40:33.183
Wanna try to finish
what our daughter started?

575
00:40:35.185 --> 00:40:36.854
Where did they take our little girl?

576
00:40:36.937 --> 00:40:39.106
Youth detention. I guess. Shit.

577
00:40:39.690 --> 00:40:42.776
What a shame.

578
00:40:45.988 --> 00:40:47.406
We'll say I did it.

579
00:40:49.950 --> 00:40:50.951
Okay? I shot you.

580
00:40:51.034 --> 00:40:52.536
You don't understand.

581
00:40:52.619 --> 00:40:54.705
Natalie found you.
I'll go to prison. okay?

582
00:40:54.788 --> 00:40:56.248
- It's an eye for an eye.
- Anna...

583
00:40:56.331 --> 00:40:58.375
Just stop.
Look. I will do whatever you want.

584
00:40:58.458 --> 00:41:01.128
This is what I wanted.

585
00:41:02.921 --> 00:41:05.966
For you to feel this.

586
00:41:06.758 --> 00:41:11.513
To feel your family ripped apart.

587
00:41:12.347 --> 00:41:13.807
Broken.

588
00:41:15.184 --> 00:41:16.852
Caged.

589
00:41:17.644 --> 00:41:19.605
Your children taken away.

590
00:41:20.480 --> 00:41:21.648
This…

591
00:41:23.859 --> 00:41:26.069
I did not take away your son.

592
00:41:26.153 --> 00:41:28.530
You killed your wife and your son.

593
00:41:29.156 --> 00:41:31.033
You destroyed your family. not me.

594
00:41:31.116 --> 00:41:34.203
Ooh. Look what a little bit of
pressure does to you.

595
00:41:34.995 --> 00:41:38.749
I will kill you. I will destroy you.
Do you understand?

596
00:41:38.832 --> 00:41:41.168
- I will kill you. I will kill you.
- Whoa. Hey. hey. hey. hey. hey.

597
00:41:41.251 --> 00:41:42.252
Security.

598
00:41:42.336 --> 00:41:46.381
Okay. Anna. go on.
Try to make sense of this life now.

599
00:41:48.175 --> 00:41:51.887
God's timing is perfect.

600
00:44:28.836 --> 00:44:31.046
Tropical Storm Wesley
became Hurricane Wesley

601
00:44:31.129 --> 00:44:33.215
and continues to grow over the Atlantic.

602
00:44:33.298 --> 00:44:36.176
Please be advised
as we continue to monitor the situation.

602
00:44:37.305 --> 00:45:37.587
